{"tid":1732624,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"狗:有殺錯無放生 尖東華懋捉60市民","createTime":"2019-11-18T02:33:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T06:25:46.000Z","uid":74778,"like":11,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"408145914c9056b5d93622170093deb04e36a15c","tid":1732624,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T02:33:37.000Z","msg":"尖東華懋捉60市民<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1492909-20191118.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1492909-20191118.htm&d=Iox0GB6uY5Umm6P4cmuVh%2FYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=4e5108f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1492909-20191118.htm&h=0e47ca42\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1492909-20191118.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n超過40名帶備圓盾、長槍等裝備的防暴警察在尖東華懋廣場外，拘捕最少60人。現場所見，被捕人士排成幾行坐在地上，警員用索帶反綁他們的雙手在背後，之後將市民分批押上警車。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息指，約100名市民早前在華懋廣場外，試圖前往理工大學，警員從科學館廣場和科學館方向兩邊夾擊，攔截大批市民。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3229d3d9be1cf0a22b8b60d4edc7c98d933fc4a","tid":1732624,"uid":92347,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T02:34:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1JKWTmg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1JKWTmg.jpg&h=333cd4ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n班狗話無入過學校"},{"pid":"c5530679fffa36f290be15859ba6a431d424bdf1","tid":1732624,"uid":125502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T02:34:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1NdgS8Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"h